column5: hoping someone could help us find the right person or company to demolish this bard and clean up the mess it's left. We are in the Brantford area. The barn was so rotted I don't think there would be much wood to reclaim, if any at all  Thanks,  Mark
call any excavation company...they will bury it onsite...
OOOOHHHHH I can bring some marshmellows if someone else brings chocolate and graham crackers for smores.
I'll bring the weiners and sticks
